# The app itself needs NO environment variables.
# Users paste their own Groq API key into the Settings modal in the UI.
# The key is stored in localStorage and sent per-request as the
# `x-groq-api-key` header.
#
# The only place .env is read is by the dev-only eval / e2e scripts:
#
#   GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...
#
# Set this if you want to run `npm run eval` or `npm run test:e2e`.
